## Production Integration

In a production environment, the generated reminder text would be sent to a Text-to-Speech (TTS) API such as:

- Amazon Polly  
- Google Cloud TTS  
- ElevenLabs  

The system workflow would be:

1. Generate reminder message  
2. Send message to TTS API  
3. Receive audio response  
4. Deliver automated voice call or notification  
5. Log delivery outcome in CRM  

